<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>شُعْبَةً،<span class="c5"> فَأَفْضَلُهَا قَوْلُ:</span> لَا إِلَهَ إِلَّا اللَّهُ، وَأَدْنَاهَا إِمَاطَةُ الْأَذَى عَنِ الطَّرِيقِ» .<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضًا صَلَّى اللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَسَلَّمَ:</span> <span class="c2">«الْحَيَاءُ شُعْبَةٌ مِنَ الْإِيمَانِ»</span> .<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضًا:</span> <span class="c2">«أَكْمَلُ الْمُؤْمِنِينَ إِيمَانًا أَحْسَنُهُمْ خُلُقًا»</span> .<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">وَقَالَ أَيْضًا:</span> <span class="c2">«الْبَذَاذَةُ مِنَ الْإِيمَانِ»</span> .<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>